==== 佔中九子案 ====
2014年11月25日，[[旺角清場及驅散行動|旺角佔領區開始清場]]，黃浩銘被捕前被警打至耳出血，後被押送上警車時警察刻意用手遮掩該耳朵。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20141128/53174881|title=之鋒：黃浩銘被打至耳出血 警刻意用手遮掩|newspaper=[[蘋果日報_(香港)|蘋果日報]]|date=2014-11-28|access-date=2015-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170820203411/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20141128/53174881|archive-date=2017-08-20|dead-url=no}}</ref> 12月10日晚，金鐘佔領區清場前夕，社民連黃浩銘被捕。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20141211/bkn-20141211121927717-1211_00822_001.html|title=黃浩銘及蘇浩因涉非法集結被捕|newspaper=[[東方日報_(香港)|東方日報]]|date=2014-12-11|access-date=2015-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924060449/http://www.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20141211/bkn-20141211121927717-1211_00822_001.html|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20141212/18966454|title=清場前警上門拘4行動派|newspaper=[[蘋果日報_(香港)|蘋果日報]]|date=2014-12-12|access-date=2015-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150712171457/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20141212/18966454|archive-date=2015-07-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 

2014年12月10日晚，金鐘佔領區清場前夕，社民連黃浩銘在正前往金鐘佔領區時，在沙田上禾輋村村口被警方以「非法集結」拘捕，翌日下午警察金鐘清場完畢，黃浩銘才在[[九龍城警署|九龍城警署]]獲取保釋，並趕赴[[葵涌警署|葵涌警署]]支持其他在金鐘佔領區被捕的示威者。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20141212/18966454|title=清場前　警上門拘4行動派|date=2014-12-12|work=Apple Daily 蘋果日報|access-date=2018-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180913150340/https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20141212/18966454|archive-date=2018-09-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>

